data.description: The perfect home with space of your own on a 1.58 acre lot! Here it is! 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, over 2100 sq. ft. all on one level! Beautifully maintained, LVP floors and carpet, new furnace and newer water heater, new interior paint and light fixtures. Covered front porch, 2-stall barn plus a 2 car garage. Central Weld District Water and 1/2 share of Godfrey Ditch for irrigation.
